com.martensigwart.fakeload

Class SystemLoad

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.martensigwart.fakeload.SystemLoad

  • @ThreadSafe
public final class SystemLoad
extends Object
    Class representing system load. This class keeps variables for representing different system load parameters like CPU, memory, disk I/O, etc. The class is thread-safe and used within the DefaultSimulationInfrastructure to aggregate FakeLoad objects that were submitted concurrently.
